name: Meltdownlove - Kharmazh Fluphworth
description:
From a triptych "The Fluphworth". Portraits of a digital cat family. 

Marzhin - mother 
Katkido - son
Kharmazh - father

A part of Meltdown Hallucinations mega series. 
Inspired by mythological creatures, ritual masks, computer animation, psychedelic art.
